"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-culture-2024-0317-1433204-bend-dont-break-irish-olympian-frank-omaras-inspiring-story\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"We present an extract fromBend Do not Break, the new memoir from Irish Olympian Frank O'Mara.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 93, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 65, \"end\": 79, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irish Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 65, \"end\": 79, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irish Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 80, \"end\": 92, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_O'Mara\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Frank O'Mara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_O'Mara\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_O'Mara\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Victory is a life well lived or a day enjoyed...\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Limerick man Frank O'Mara had the athletics career most only dream of, competing for Ireland in three Olympic Games and breaking Irish and world records.\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 145, \"end\": 153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limerick\", \"score\": 0.9914226558431706, \"rank\": 0.008651539264235916, \"text\": \"Limerick\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limerick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limerick\"}, {\"begin\": 158, \"end\": 170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_O'Mara\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Frank O'Mara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_O'Mara\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frank_O'Mara\"}, {\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999610330417309, \"rank\": 3.89684758502045e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_language\", \"score\": 0.583898811325916, \"rank\": 0.7071575593771311, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After his retirement from running, he settled in the US with his family and made his way to the top of the telecoms industry.\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997228010476079, \"rank\": 0.00016593109641768327, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, at age forty-eight, his life changed forever when he was diagnosed with early onset Parkinson's disease.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The progression was rapid, causing severe muscle cramps, tremors, and eventually the inability to walk and at times even speak.\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In this inspiring memoir, Frank recounts his battle with Parkinson's.\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes you have to accept the unbelievable  The event that finally forced me to face reality did not happen in a doctor's office or a hospital.\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not feel the true weight of my diagnosis until my friend Gary Taylor came over to check on us at home.\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 946, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Taylor_(scholar)\", \"score\": 0.8871351948527195, \"rank\": 0.0812243502051856, \"text\": \"Gary Taylor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Taylor_(scholar)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gary_Taylor_(scholar)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gary was aware that I'd been struggling with some sort of malady for months.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He'd followed my effort to treat my issue as a sports injury.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When my sports medicine specialist said it might be a little more complicated than that, I saw a spine-doctor to rule out spinal stenosis.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Next up, the neurologist.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gary knew I'd seen a neurologist earlier that week, but he did not know what, if anything, we'd learned.\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1402, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The doctor had performed what seemed to be perfunctory tests, nothing elaborate: routine hand motions, finger tapping, foot stomping, and basic balance and gait tests.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The exam only lasted about ten minutes.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The doctor's response had been quick and precise.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have seen this often enough to recognise it.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a slowness in your movement on the left side.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sorry to have to tell you this.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have Parkinson's disease.'\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I took his assessment with a degree of scepticism.\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'What baffles me is, I came in with a running problem and I am leaving with an old person's neurological disease,' I said.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The doctor just shook his head, but I pressed on.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am only forty-eight years old.'\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The doctor had then proposed a way I might postpone reality a little longer.\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I suggest that you take a drug called Sinemet, which is used to treat the symptoms of the disease,' he said.\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'If you see an improvement, then you know you have Parkinson's.\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do not, then you know I am wrong.'\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not know Dr Archer very well at that point, but I appreciated that he refrained from adding, 'I think you will find that I am right.'\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2408, \"end\": 2414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Archer\", \"score\": 0.9999970917375774, \"rank\": 2.9082708837433126e-06, \"text\": \"Archer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Archer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Archer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then, I have given him many opportunities to say, 'I told you so,' but he never has.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On my way home from the neurologist, I had called my wife, Patty, and rattled on about having no visible symptoms, so what improvement would I even look for?\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2681, \"end\": 2686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"score\": 0.9999998900802953, \"rank\": 1.0991982775465412e-07, \"text\": \"Patty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She humoured me, which only served as reinforcement in my confused mind.\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As I saw it, I was just trying to get to the bottom of a chronic injury that prevented me from running and was now beginning to interfere with my walking.\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 3007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not have a single symptom the doctor could point to,' I persisted.\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not even have a tremor!'\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As usual, Patty gave wise counsel.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3124, \"end\": 3129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"score\": 0.9999998900802953, \"rank\": 1.0991982775465412e-07, \"text\": \"Patty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Why do not I pick up the medicine this afternoon, and you can give it a go like he's suggested?'\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"she said.\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3256, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Why do not you try it?'\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3281, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a few days later that Gary came by.\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3325, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was upstairs when I heard him knock on the front door.\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I looked out the window and saw his truck parked out front.\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought he'd come by to discuss the startup of a running store.\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn't a great fan of retail, so I was a little anxious about the conversation.\", \"from\": 3509, \"to\": 3590, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It took me a few minutes to finish what I was doing, then I headed down to the kitchen.\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As I descended the stairs, I heard voices and what sounded like sobbing.\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I stopped for a moment to listen and heard Gary's voice above my wife's muffled crying.\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I listened a little while longer, but their hushed voices were indecipherable.\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 3919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I continued down to the landing and turned the corner into the kitchen.\", \"from\": 3920, \"to\": 3991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Neither Gary nor Patty had heard me coming and my sudden appearance surprised them.\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4009, \"end\": 4014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"score\": 0.9999998900802953, \"rank\": 1.0991982775465412e-07, \"text\": \"Patty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt like I'd crashed the party.\", \"from\": 4077, \"to\": 4111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The look on both their faces said it all.\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4153, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could tell they were guilty of some deceit.\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4199, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gary had his arm around Patty.\", \"from\": 4200, \"to\": 4230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4224, \"end\": 4229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"score\": 0.9999998900802953, \"rank\": 1.0991982775465412e-07, \"text\": \"Patty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I had not known them both so well, I would have thought they were about to admit to a clandestine affair.\", \"from\": 4231, \"to\": 4339, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I almost excused myself for interrupting.\", \"from\": 4340, \"to\": 4381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Confused, uncertain what emotion to deploy, I just peered at them.\", \"from\": 4382, \"to\": 4448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will never forget the stricken looks on their faces.\", \"from\": 4449, \"to\": 4503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gary saw my perplexed stare and broke the silence.\", \"from\": 4505, \"to\": 4555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'God, I am so sorry, Frank!'\", \"from\": 4556, \"to\": 4584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was then I realised what they were trying to hide from me.\", \"from\": 4586, \"to\": 4647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Patty had told Gary about my doctor's visit earlier in the week.\", \"from\": 4648, \"to\": 4712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4648, \"end\": 4653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"score\": 0.9999998900802953, \"rank\": 1.0991982775465412e-07, \"text\": \"Patty\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patty_and_Selma\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So, you heard the news, did you?'\", \"from\": 4714, \"to\": 4748, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I blurted out.\", \"from\": 4749, \"to\": 4763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I did, and I feel awful for both of you,' Gary replied.\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then he hugged me.\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 4841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was one of those long hugs, the kind given when no words are readily available.\", \"from\": 4842, \"to\": 4924, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gary clinched tighter before he released me.\", \"from\": 4925, \"to\": 4969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'You are strong,' he said.\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 4997, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'You got this.'\", \"from\": 4998, \"to\": 5013, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to impress on him my disbelief, to tell him how wrong the doctor must have been, how little evidence there was to support the diagnosis.\", \"from\": 5015, \"to\": 5160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After all, Gary was a runner and should know about injuries.\", \"from\": 5161, \"to\": 5221, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But there was a firmness in his eyes and a resolve in his voice that caused me to repress the urge.\", \"from\": 5222, \"to\": 5321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was nothing else to do except cry.\", \"from\": 5323, \"to\": 5363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We sobbed.\", \"from\": 5364, \"to\": 5374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their faces shocked me to my core.\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was especially horrifying to see my beautiful wife look so worried.\", \"from\": 5411, \"to\": 5481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She had accepted my disbelief because she knew it might take time to accept, let alone digest the news.\", \"from\": 5482, \"to\": 5585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the other hand, she had no reason to disbelieve the doctor.\", \"from\": 5586, \"to\": 5648, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was the moment I knew I was facing a monstrous challenge.\", \"from\": 5649, \"to\": 5711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not keep reality at bay any longer.\", \"from\": 5712, \"to\": 5755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had early onset Parkinson's disease at the age of forty-eight.\", \"from\": 5757, \"to\": 5821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bend Do not Breakis published by The O'Brien Press    \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 5825, \"to\": 5890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 5891, \"to\": 5981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5916, \"end\": 5939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851270567, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 5941, \"end\": 5948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999610330417309, \"rank\": 3.89684758502045e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9 is not responsible for the content of external internet sites.\", \"from\": 5982, \"to\": 6048, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5982, \"end\": 5985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Images Courtesy of Getty Images.\", \"from\": 6050, \"to\": 6082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6069, \"end\": 6074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999856791225731, \"rank\": 9.519655590161297e-06, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}]}]}"